<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%- typeof title !== 'undefined' ? `${title} | ` : '' %>QRISKITA</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />
  <link
    rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"
    crossorigin="anonymous"
  />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= url('/css/tailwind.css') %>" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= url('/css/app.css') %>" />

  <style>
    :root {
      --brand-700: #15803d;
      --brand-600: #16a34a;
      --brand-500: #22c55e;
      --brand-400: #4ade80;
      --brand-50:  #f0fdf4;
      --ink:       #0f172a;
      --ink-muted: #64748b;
      --line:      #e2e8f0;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    html, body {
      min-height: 100%;
      margin: 0;
    }

    body.qris-auth-shell {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: "Inter", "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    /* ── Left brand panel ─────────────────────────── */
    .auth-aside {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 56px 52px;
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, #166534 0%, #15803d 45%, #16a34a 100%);
    }

    .auth-aside::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      right: -140px;
      bottom: -140px;
      width: 460px;
      height: 460px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

    .auth-aside::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      right: 40px;
      top: -120px;
      width: 320px;
      height: 320px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }

    .auth-aside-brand {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .auth-aside-mark {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      color: var(--brand-700);
      background: #fff;
    }

    .auth-aside-brand strong {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    }

    .auth-aside-copy {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 380px;
    }

    .auth-aside-copy h2 {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      font-size: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .auth-aside-copy p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
    }

    .auth-aside-list {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .auth-aside-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    }

    .auth-aside-list i {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 26px;
      height: 26px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
    }

    /* ── Right form panel ─────────────────────────── */
    .auth-main {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }

    .auth-card {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 400px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      body.qris-auth-shell {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .auth-aside {
        display: none;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="qris-auth-shell">
  <aside class="auth-aside">
    <div class="auth-aside-brand">
      <div class="auth-aside-mark">QK</div>
      <strong>QRISKITA</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="auth-aside-copy">
      <h2>Konsol Admin Merchant</h2>
      <p>Kelola transaksi, mutasi, dan settlement QRIS dalam satu dasbor yang aman dan terpadu.</p>
    </div>

    <ul class="auth-aside-list">
      <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Pemantauan transaksi real-time</li>
      <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Rekonsiliasi mutasi otomatis</li>
      <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Akses aman untuk operator internal</li>
    </ul>
  </aside>

  <main class="auth-main">
    <div class="auth-card">
      <%- body %>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
